latestIgtvVideos.title: My Wedding LookBook  Our Destination Wedding
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This video is really close to my heart as I share my wedding with everyone. 

Ours was a Destination Wedding at Jim Corbett, Uttarakhand and everything to the T was planned by me and my husband personally. In this video, I share with you all the details of my Wedding Outfits, Makeup and more. 

It's a very candid narration about all my wedding functions. I really have put my heart and soul to this 😊

I believe it's the perfect time to celebrate 2000 subscribers on my YouTube Channel with this video so I really hope you enjoy this video.
